title: Maps of Foreclosed Homes by State
description:
Maps of Foreclosed Homes by State

These files are maps viewable with Google Earth.  See bank-owned properties discounted up to 30-50%.  Included are 52 maps, one for each state in the United States.

You must have Google Earth installed to view these data files.  Google Earth is free mapping software available here: <a href=" http://earth.google.com" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://earth.google.com</a>

After installing Google Earth, click on one of the KMZ files included in this torrent to view all foreclosed homes for a particular state.

TIP: Turn on Street View in Google Earth to see full 360 degree panormic views when viewing the property!

This data is the only free source on the Internet that let's you use Google Earth to browse foreclosed properties.


Enjoy!
